  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Living Log/DST</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\">\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Living Logs</b> are <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Items</a> dropped by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Treeguard\" title=\"Treeguard\">Treeguards</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Poison_Birchnut_Tree\" title=\"Poison Birchnut Tree\">Poison Birchnut Trees</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mush_Gnome\" title=\"Mush Gnome\">Mush Gnomes</a>. They can also be obtained by <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Axe\" title=\"Axe\">chopping</a> down <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Totally_Normal_Tree\" title=\"Totally Normal Tree\">Totally Normal Trees</a>, the stump of Totally Normal Tree can be dug for another Living Log. <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wormwood\" title=\"Wormwood\">Wormwood</a> can always &quot;craft&quot; Living Logs at the cost of 20 Health. \n</p><p>They are used to craft several magic items, including a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shadow_Manipulator\" title=\"Shadow Manipulator\">Shadow Manipulator</a>, and can also be used as fuel for a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fire\" title=\"Fire\">Fire</a>. Living Logs will scream when burned on a fire or when eaten by a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookie_Cutter\" title=\"Cookie Cutter\">Cookie Cutter</a>.\n</p><p>A Living Log may be used to repair a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wood_Wall\" title=\"Wood Wall\">Wood Wall</a>. This works in a similar fashion to using a standard log, except that the Living Log repairs three times the wall health of a standard log.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Living_Log\" title=\"Living Log\"><img alt=\"Living Log.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Living_Log.png?bdc25f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Silk\" title=\"Silk\"><img alt=\"Silk.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Silk.png?22ef7f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butterfly_Wings\" title=\"Butterfly Wings\"><img alt=\"Butterfly Wings.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Butterfly_Wings.png?b14761\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>68</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Alchemy_Engine\" title=\"Alchemy Engine\"><img alt=\"Alchemy Engine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Alchemy_Engine.png/42px-Alchemy_Engine.png?937c5f\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Glossamer_Saddle\" title=\"Glossamer Saddle\"><img alt=\"Glossamer Saddle.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Glossamer_Saddle.png?d6dfad\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Living_Log\" title=\"Living Log\"><img alt=\"Living Log.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Living_Log.png?bdc25f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Purple_Gem\" title=\"Purple Gem\"><img alt=\"Purple Gem.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Purple_Gem.png?ca6f08\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=