.gg/wiki/Arboretum_Experiment\" title=\"Arboretum Experiment\"><img alt=\"Totally Normal Root.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Totally_Normal_Root.png?4f04f8\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><i>Only during the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Category:Events\" title=\"Category:Events\">Event</a>:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hallowed_Nights\" title=\"Hallowed Nights\"><img alt=\"Hallowed Nights icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hallowed_Nights_icon.png/50px-Hallowed_Nights_icon.png?eed524\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hallowed_Nights\" title=\"Hallowed Nights\">Hallowed Nights</a><br></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>The Living Log&#x27;s scream was added in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Version_History#April_20,_2013_-_The_End_of_the_Beginning.5B3.5D\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Version History\">The End of the Beginning</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Living_Log/DST#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Living_Log/DST#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
