  "wikitext": "{{Navbutton/Separation}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|hpRestored = 0\n|hungerRestored = 0\n|sanityRestored = 0\n|foodType =[[Food_Type/DST#Wood|Wood]] [[File:Wood_Type_Icon.png|25px|link=Food_Type/DST#Wood]]<br>(non-survivor food)\n|image = Living Log Dropped.png\n|icon = Living Log.png\n|stack = 20\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 45 sec.\n|canBeBurned=1\n|droppedBy = {{pic|24|Treeguard}} {{pic|32|Totally Normal Tree}} {{pic|24|Poison Birchnut Tree}} {{pic24|Mush Gnome}}\n\n|crafting_infobox =\n<tabber>\nWormwood=\n{{Craft Infobox\n|craft_desctiption = ''Put yourself into your work.''\n|tier = 0\n|filter = {{Pic32|Refined Materials Filter}} {{Pic32|Wormwood Filter}}\n|ingredient1 = Health Decrease\n|multiplier1 = 20 ({{Pic|28|Wormwood Portrait|Wormwood}} only)\n}}\n|-|\nWandering Trader=\n{{Craft Infobox\n|craft_desctiption =''Life wood be a scream...''\n|crafting_text = {{Pic32|Beefalo Wool}}x3 \n|tier_text = {{Pic32|Wandering Trader}}\n|filter      = {{Pic32|Trading Filter}}\n}}\n</tabber>\n|spawnCode = \"livinglog\"}}\n\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = It looks worried.\n|willow = It looks upset.\n|wolfgang = Creepy face log!\n|wendy = It is forever screaming silently.\n|wx78 = EVEN WORSE THAN A NORMAL LOG\n|wickerbottom = This log is special.\n|woodie = I want to keep you, and call you \"Frank\".\n|maxwell = I like the noise they make when you burn them.\n|wigfrid = Burning such magic wöuld seem a waste.\n|webber = This log has a face.\n|winona = Stop looking at me like that.\n|warly = Magic building blocks!\n|wortox = Don't look at me with those sad eyes!\n|wormwood = Friend. Nice friend\n|wurt = Feel kinda bad, florp...\n|walter = Yep, this log's definitely haunted.\n|wanda = This log is a lot livelier than it should be.\n|choose = woodie\n}}\n\n'''Living Logs''' are [[Item]]s dropped by [[Treeguard]]s, [[Poison Birchnut Tree]]s and [[Mush Gnome]]s. They can also be obtained by [[Axe|chopping]] down [[Totally Normal Tree]]s, the stump of Totally Normal Tree can be dug for another Living Log. [[Wormwood]] can always \"craft\" Living Logs at the cost of 20 Health. \n\nThey are used to craft several magic items, including a [[Shadow Manipulator]], and can also be used as fuel for a [[Fire]]. Living Logs will scream when burned on a fire or when eaten by a [[Cookie Cutter]].\n\nA Living Log may be used to repair a [[Wood Wall]]. This works in a similar fashion to using a standard log, except that the Living Log repairs three times the wall health of a standard log.\n\n=={{pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Silk\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Butterfly Wings\n|count3 = 68\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Glossamer Saddle}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Purple Gem\n|item3 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count3 = 7\n|tool = Prestihatitator\n|result = Shadow Manipulator}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 5\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Dark Sword}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Batilisk Wing\n|coun21 = 3\n|item1 = Living Log\n|coun12 = 2\n|item3 = Purple Gem\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Bat Bat}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Purple Gem\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Telelocator Staff}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Gold Nugget\n|count3 = 8\n|tool = Shadow Manipulator\n|result = Telelocator Focus}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Yellow Gem\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Broken Pseudoscience Station\n|result = Star Caller's Staff}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Green Gem\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Broken Pseudoscience Station\n|result = Deconstruction Staff}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Thulecite\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Ancient Pseudoscience Station\n|result = Thulecite Club}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Stinger\n|count2 = 4\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|result = Bramble Husk\n|character = Wormwood\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Stinger\n|count2 = 1\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 1\n|result = Bramble Trap\n|character = Wormwood\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|item2 = Mourning Glory\n|count2 = 3\n|result = Distilled Vengeance\n|character=Wendy}}\n\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 2\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 1\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Applied Silviculture\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Papyrus\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Feather Pencil\n|count3 = 1\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Bookcase\n|character = Wickerbottom}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Time Pieces\n|item3 = Bone Shards\n|count3 = 4\n|result = Second Chance Watch\n|character = Wanda\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Cut Grass\n|count2 = 3\n|item1 = Living Log\n|count1 = 2\n|item3 = Nightmare Fuel\n|count3 = 5\n|result = Treeguard Idol\n|character = Woodie\n|skill = Treeguard Feller III\n}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Living Log\n|item2 = Batilisk Wing\n|item3 = Sanity Decrease\n|count3 = 20\n|tool = Mad Scientist Lab\n|result = Arboretum Experiment\n|note ={{Event|Hallowed Nights}} \n}}\n\n=={{pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia==\n* The Living Log's scream was added in the ''[[Version History#April 20, 2013 - The End of the Beginning.5B3.5D|The End of the Beginning]]'' update.\n<tabber>\nResources=\n{{Resources}}\n|-|\nCraftable Items=\n{{Craftable Items and Structures on DST}}\n</tabber>\n[[de:Lebender Baumstamm]]\n[[es:Tronco viviente]]\n[[fr:bûche vivante]]\n[[vi:Gỗ Sống]]\n[[Category:Mob Dropped Items]]\n[[Category:Boss Dropped Items]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Refined Materials Filter]]\n[[Category:Survivor Items Filter]]\n__NOTOC__"
